Straight through- top talking to bottom (ex. router to switch =straight / router to hub= straight / PC seever to switch= straight..
.. PC server to hub= straight / switch to hub= straight )
Cross- if in the same layer (ex. router to router= cross / router to PC server= cross / PC to PC= cross / hub to hub= cross..
.. switch to switch= cross 
Rollover- 
Outband management= physical, walk to switch to physically connect to console to manage the switch 
